{"tid":2157150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(香港是Condom) 歐盟已決定制裁Belarus官員","createTime":"2020-08-14T23:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T03:34:25.000Z","uid":14918,"like":32,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2406f3271d50f91bd5fc03d5d541d333cc3240f5","tid":2157150,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:34:52.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】歐盟周五（14日）開始展開制裁白俄羅斯的程序，指出白俄總統盧卡申科在具爭議性的選舉中連任後，隨即鐵腕打壓示威，情况惹「嚴重關注」。歐盟外長昨同意擬定制裁白俄官員名單。德國外長馬斯昨會後向記者稱，歐盟外長已決定制裁要為鎮壓負責的白俄官員。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟於2004年首次因當地反對派人士及記者失蹤等違反人權問題制裁白俄，當中許多制裁措施於2016年白俄釋放部分政治犯後解除，但武器禁運仍生效。新一輪制裁料涉旅遊禁令及資產凍結等。歐盟周五將舉行外長視像會議，《衛報》引述歐盟消息指，這場會議應可初步達成制裁的政治決定，但具體法律細節則要等到本月底面對面外長會議再敲定。<br />\n<br />\n料涉旅遊禁令資產凍結 至少9國同意<br />\n<br />\n路透社披露，目前已有最少9國同意制裁白俄，包括波蘭、捷克、愛沙尼亞、丹麥等。匈牙利或是最大障礙，但歐盟消息指其初步不反對制裁，但或試圖縮窄制裁人數範圍。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200815/s00014/1597430881297/%e6%ad%90%e7%9b%9f%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a%e5%88%b6%e8%a3%81%e7%99%bd%e4%bf%84%e5%ae%98%e5%93%a1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200815%2Fs00014%2F1597430881297%2F%25e6%25ad%2590%25e7%259b%259f%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a%25e5%2588%25b6%25e8%25a3%2581%25e7%2599%25bd%25e4%25bf%2584%25e5%25ae%2598%25e5%2593%25a1&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8YVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=ada0f057\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200815%2Fs00014%2F1597430881297%2F%25e6%25ad%2590%25e7%259b%259f%25e6%25b1%25ba%25e5%25ae%259a%25e5%2588%25b6%25e8%25a3%2581%25e7%2599%25bd%25e4%25bf%2584%25e5%25ae%2598%25e5%2593%25a1&h=16fac642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200815/s00014/1597430881297/%e6%ad%90%e7%9b%9f%e6%b1%ba%e5%ae%9a%e5%88%b6%e8%a3%81%e7%99%bd%e4%bf%84%e5%ae%98%e5%93%a1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3d8e479fa1d162a16b38072b1bbe5ad68dc8d9","tid":2157150,"uid":365464,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:39:44.000Z","msg":"不過又咁講，佢哋都含左盧卡申科條撚廿鳩幾年，都希望佢哋成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c699fd0a2c04a96faa3ca1a2d18cc7ff0d3e29d","tid":2157150,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:57:51.000Z","msg":"歐盟應機未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRubio去信歐盟要求聯合制裁推動港區國安法官員<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2156733\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2156733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"70ff6cef5065650c93e9b299cc0d1ee738f0bf34","tid":2157150,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:59:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf60d325ba86735c97ba2bfd40cabeb661d8a5f9","tid":2157150,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T00:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515453732ce7e2ea26088b5651665f37913d48e9","tid":2157150,"uid":306614,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4c699fd0a2c04a96faa3ca1a2d18cc7ff0d3e29d","tid":2157150,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:57:51.000Z","msg":"歐盟應機未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hk